<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL17">
<l>virumpiniṉ ṟētta māṭṭēṉ vitiyilēṉ matiyoṉ ṟillai</l>
<l>irumpupōl valiya neñca miṟaiyiṟai yurukum vaṇṇañ</l>
<l>curumpamar cōlai cūḻnta varaṅkamā kōyil koṇṭa</l>
<l>karumpiṉaik kaṇṭu koṇṭeṉ kaṇṇiṇai kaḷikku māṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I do not keep praise [Him] with desire; I do not have [any] good fortune;</l>
<l>I do not have any knowledge.</l>
<l>How come my pair of eyes rejoice beholding the Sugarcane</l>
<l>who took up abode in the great temple Raṅgam surrounded by groves with bees,</l>
<l>in such a way that [my] steel-like hard heart melts little by little!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
